test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -8836 == -94
 +  where -8836 = <built-in function prod>([-2, -47, -94])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (0 == 3)
 +  where 0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7c2e2e096d80>([-94])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7c2e2e096d80> = [[1, -94], [1, -94, 1], [-94, 1], [-94, 1, -94], [1, -94], [1, -94, 1], ...].count
